pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">行业资质</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.8%; border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-image: initial; border-left: none; background: #c00000; padding: 0cm; height: 16.5pt; line-height: 2;\" width=\"48%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">特殊资质及要求</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 13.46%; border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"13\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"13%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">鲜花/奢侈品</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 12.08%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">奢侈品</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 13.7%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"13%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 11.98%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"11%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 48.8%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;\" rowspan=\"13\" width=\"48%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.95pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">奢侈品类目准入品牌清单：</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.95pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://helpcenter.jd.com/vender/issue/45202.html\">https://helpcenter.jd.com/vender/issue/45202.html</a>，其中COACH品牌采取邀约入驻。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.95pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">．奢侈品<span style=\"color: #000000;\">类目</span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">入驻旗舰店和卖场店开放TM标入驻且TM标申请时间至入驻审核时间必须大于6个月</span> ，专卖店和专营店开放TM标入驻，且TM标注册申请时间至入驻开店审核时间必须大于3个月，TM标有效期请填写申请日期加2年后的日期，R标有效期按商标注册证有效日期填写。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.95pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">专卖店、专营店需有3级以内（包括3级）的完整授权链路。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.95pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">委托进口协议（经营进口商品）：报关单上的收货人和消费使用单位不在授权链上，需提供委托报关授权。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.95pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">5.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">报关单（经营进口商品）：奢侈品类目需提供近1年内的中华人民共和国海关进口货物报关单，其他类目需提供近3年内的中华人民共和国海关进口货物报关单，报关单上应展现对应品牌名称及商品名称。</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.08%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 16.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">花艺服务</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 13.7%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 16.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"13%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">花艺服务</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 11.98%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 16.5pt;\" rowspan=\"11\" width=\"11%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">/</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 12.08%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 16.5pt;\" rowspan=\"11\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"12%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">鲜花</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 13.7%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 16.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"13%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">永生花</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 13.7%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt; height: 16.5pt;\" nowrap=\"nowrap\" width=\"13%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">婚庆鲜花</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"width: 13.7%; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-right: solid windowtext 1.0pt; paddin